      • _getLastModified

        protected long _getLastModified(RenderContext rc,
                                javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest req)
                         throws java.io.IOException
        Get the last mod time. Also compares the etag header.
        Parameters:
        rc - the render context.
        req - the http request.
        Returns:
        the last mod time or -1 if unknown or the etag comparison indicates a change in the resource since last served.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an error occurs processing the request.
